{"tid":1129301,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C朗歷史第一人連續10年分別係2個三大聯賽都入20球","createTime":"2019-04-28T11:45:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T02:46:37.000Z","uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"038d97db13c33c581e976c19322f54b8690a9a69","tid":1129301,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T11:45:09.000Z","msg":"你倒是給個準信兒啊，到底火幾年？<br />\n<br />\n  C.朗拿度在對國際米蘭的比賽中攻入一球後，過去10個賽季的聯賽入球數都達到或超過20個。<br />\n<br />\n  今季C.朗拿度已經為祖雲達斯在意甲攻入20球，效力皇馬和祖記的近10個賽季，他每個賽季的聯賽入球數都達到或超過了20個。<br />\n<br />\n  2014/15賽季，他為皇馬在西甲攻入48球，創近10年聯賽入球最高紀錄。此外，他在職業生涯的各項賽事中已經狂入600球，真是一台入球機器。"},{"pid":"fd46d9ca0616d074d2b6b2b2c759788c2ed0e605","tid":1129301,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T11:45:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MJpq2bq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMJpq2bq.jpg&h=41a0a211&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6dac4fce6c80ddcfb15ee993861b1df596867dec","tid":1129301,"uid":74262,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T11:49:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ff47a953d62e1e0db2b3b7c762645d7bdaedadb6","tid":1129301,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6dac4fce6c80ddcfb15ee993861b1df596867dec","tid":1129301,"uid":74262,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T11:49:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T12:21:14.000Z","msg":"唔通德甲咩"},{"pid":"636137e05e3f55fb7ae5de24660680629b252240","tid":1129301,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd46d9ca0616d074d2b6b2b2c759788c2ed0e605","tid":1129301,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T11:45:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MJpq2bq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMJpq2bq.jpg&h=41a0a211&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T12:31:37.000Z","msg":"佢08已經20+ la wor, 唔計埋?"},